// CreateNodeDialog
// Modal dialog for creating a new node in the SMACH diagram editor.
// Collects node ID, label, and type, then calls onCreate.

FUNCTION CreateNodeDialog(onClose, onCreate, existingNodeIds) -> JSX   EXPORT
  Tracks nodeId, label, nodeType fields plus validation errors.
  Validates: nodeId non-empty, no whitespace, not already in existingNodeIds.
  Confirms on Enter (in any field) or OK button. Cancels on Escape or Cancel.
  Calls onCreate({nodeId, label, nodeType}) on valid submit.
